## /GREEN — Greenfield Project Framework
For starting brand new projects, follow the 9-step workflow at `~/Github/Settings/README.md`. Type `/greenfield` to invoke. Reference `~/Github/Settings/PLAYBOOK.md` for decision defaults and lessons learned.

Workflow: `/office-hours` → write `DESIGN.md` → `/plan-ceo-review` → `/plan-eng-review` → `/plan-design-review` → reconcile against /office-hours doc → capture prompts → pre-build kill gates → cleanup before first code.

After each project ships, append lessons to `~/Github/Settings/PLAYBOOK.md` and commit — it's a living artifact.
